hould report if there's been a state change, but I'm not sure what the previous state was to compare against. Given the ambiguity, I think the safest approach is to stay silent unless something clearly needs attention, since the rules emphasize minimizing noise to Khuowgn's chat unless there's an actual issue.","thinkingSignature":"b3302eee87aedc1e2297d4523004a45d8ca5886366576fd501f319b3b1bea2df"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2074,"output":518,"cacheRead":15973,"cacheWrite":437,"totalTokens":19002,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776140744404,"responseId":"062cf4c996854b39f951b16c933f9934"}}
