json` (last check: 12:16 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Key monitored sessions:**\nSystem: - `cron:ed2d0b5d` — running ✅ (last seen 12:16 UTC, still running)\nSystem: - `cron:6f3323ef` — running ✅ (this session, 12:18 UTC)\nSystem: - `telegram:group:-5163901258` — running ✅ (last seen 12:14 UTC, still running)\nSystem: - `telegram:group:-5168104492` — done ✅\nSystem: - `telegram:direct:6053576134` — done ✅\nSystem: - `main` — done ✅\nSystem: - `cron:e7885813` — aborted ✅ (zombie cleared in last cycle)\nSystem: - `cron:b653a6c0` — stale (pre-existing, no new activity)\nSystem: - `cron:ac986a8d` — stale zombie (pre-existing)\nSystem: \nSystem: **Assessment:** No new changes detected. All sessions stable. Pipeline healthy. Silent exit.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 12:21:48 UTC] Comparing current state vs. lastHeartbeat (11:45 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Key monitored sessions:**\nSystem: - `cron:ed2d0b5d` — still running ✅ (this current session)\nSystem: - `cron:6f3323ef` — still running ✅\nSystem: - `telegram:direct:6053576134` — done ✅\nSystem: - `telegram:group:-5163901258` — done ✅\nSystem: - Pre-existing stale sessions: `cron:b653a6c0`, `cron:ac986a8d` — unchanged\nSystem: \nSystem: **No new changes detected.** All stable. Silent exit.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 12:24:19 UTC] Heartbeat state updated. **Silent exit — no changes detected.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 12:27:00 UTC] No changes detected. All sessions stable — silent exit.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 12:29:20 UTC] No changes detected. Silent exit.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 12:29 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 12:29 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776169810142}}
