lures. No new sessions spawned. No sessions died. No blockers. Pipeline stable.**\nSystem: \nSystem: Silent.\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:27:13 UTC] Comparing current state (00:26 UTC) against baseline from `heartbeat-state.json` (00:14 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Baseline:** cron:ed2d0b5d ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ cron:6f3323ef ✅ cron:53c5832a done ✅ main done ✅ telegram:direct done ✅ telegram:group:-5163901258 running ✅ — Pipeline HEALTHY, blockers: none\nSystem: \nSystem: **Current (00:26 UTC):** All 4 crons still running. telegram:direct restarted but still running. No new failures. No new sessions. No blockers.\nSystem: \nSystem: **No meaningful change detected. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:29:55 UTC] Baseline (00:14 UTC) vs current (00:29 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Baseline running:** cron:ed2d0b5d ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ cron:6f3323ef ✅ — same 3 crons still running  \nSystem: **Baseline ended:** telegram:direct ended ~22:02 UTC — new instance of same session started ~00:22 UTC (same session type, natural restart cycle)  \nSystem: **No failures. No new tasks. No blockers. Pipeline HEALTHY.**\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent — nothing to report.**\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:32:15 UTC] **Baseline vs Current (00:31 UTC):**\nSystem: \nSystem: **Baseline running (00:14 UTC):** cron:ed2d0b5d ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ cron:6f3323ef ✅ — same 3 crons still running  \nSystem: **Baseline ended:** telegram:direct ended ~22:02 UTC — brief new instance ran ~00:22–00:24 UTC (reported last cycle) — now ended again  \nSystem: **QLHV group:** ended ~22:55 UTC — no active instance — baseline already noted it had ended by 00:14\nSystem: \nSystem: **No new failures. No new tasks. No blockers. Pipeline HEALTHY.**\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent — nothing material has changed since the last report.**\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:36:08 UTC] Silent. No material changes since last check.\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:37:22 UTC] Silent. No material changes since the last report at 22:55 UTC. Three cron sessions still running (`ed2d