{"type":"message","id":"4f9a3d4d","parentId":"c0e05e43","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:29:33.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time is 04:29 UTC. Let me check sessions and update state. The system has been very active overnight with the Lead working on ahv-openclaw-setup. The nightly silence period (23:00-07:00 UTC+7) is 23:00-07:00 UTC = 16:00-04:00 UTC. Wait that's not right. UTC+7 is 7 hours ahead of UTC. So 23:00 UTC+7 = 16:00 UTC. And 07:00 UTC+7 = 00:00 UTC.\n\nSo night silence is 16:00 UTC to 00:00 UTC. Current time is 04:29 UTC which is 11:29 UTC+7. \n\nThis is outside the night silence window, so I should continue with the heartbeat. I'm seeing a stable pipeline with the core cron jobs running normally and the Lead actively working, so I'll acknowledge and update the state.","thinkingSignature":"df187208261e28c2f2a6a4a18f9628a80f29ba00490e47cadfe57fe4ec22a59f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_edj8qa0m428c_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":5,"activeMinutes":10,"messageLimit":0}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2752,"output":244,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":106847,"totalTokens":117621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776227362060,"responseId":"062e4723ceb0d48bb1b516ec8d442877"}}
