{"type":"message","id":"69bf6251","parentId":"54e4ed5c","timestamp":"2026-04-15T09:31:53.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Lead is now active via openclaw-tui. The MEMORY.md loaded into my context confirms I'm Orbis (master-orchestrator) with session reset note. The Lead's question \"bạn config loôi gì đây\" was asking about what context/config was loaded.\n\nLet me respond directly to the Lead about what MEMORY.md contains and the current state. This is not a heartbeat response - this is an actual conversation with the Lead.\n\nCurrent state:\n- MEMORY.md loaded: AHV DTLX + QLHV active, DTLX BE running port 5555, DTLX FE running port 3000, 18/18 API endpoints passing\n\n\n- Pending tasks: QLHV BE MR !6 awaiting Lead review\n- Pipeline healthy, 3 cron sessions running\n- Some abandoned cron sessions still lingering that need cleanup\n\nNow I'll address the Lead's question directly.","thinkingSignature":"db00e36849b5d282b966bccce3389fdd30ac3511d14ad83ddd855c15f0dd9ac7"},{"type":"text","text":"Xin chào Lead! Đây là Orbis (master-orchestrator) — session đã reset sau migration v4 ecosystem.\n\n**MEMORY.md đang load:**\n- **AHV DTLX**: BE running port 5555 ✅, FE port 3000 ✅, 18/18 API endpoints passing ✅\n- **QLHV**: MR !6 đang chờ Lead review/merge\n- **AHV Works**: 13 P0 issues pending\n- **Pending blockers**: JWT `doc.id → doc._id` bug trong token.service.js (DTLX) chưa fix\n\n**Pipeline hiện tại:**\n- 5p QLHV cron ✅ | 5p DTLX cron ✅ | Agent Status ✅\n- MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\n**Cần xác nhận từ Lead:**\n1. **Tắt heartbeat poll liên tục?** Hiện tạo quá nhiều cron instances (~60+/giờ)\n2. Hoặc giữ nguyên để monitor liên tục?\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1377,"output":436,"cacheRead":142861,"cacheWrite":1898,"totalTokens":146572,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":